<doc id="1243083" wikidata="Q6980835" url="?curid=1243083" title="Naturally (Three Dog Night album)">
<text>Naturally is the fifth album by American rock band Three Dog Night, released in 1970. It produced two top ten hits: &quot;Joy to the World&quot; (#1 in February 1971) and &quot;Liar&quot; (#7). &quot;One Man Band&quot; reached the top 20 (#19). The only original by the band is the instrumental &quot;Fire Eater&quot;.

