<doc id="1243350" wikidata="Q5653493" url="?curid=1243350" title="Hara (band)">
<text>Hara is a Romanian pop-rock band from Cluj-Napoca. Its members during 2000–2002 were: Flavius Buzilă, Mihai Pop, Nicu Lichirie, Tudor Runcanu and Doru Dejeu. Since 2003 the members are: Flavius Buzilă, Mihai Pop, Nicu Lichirie, Marius Astilean and Vasi Nani.

== Band members ==
Hara&#x27;s current members are:

* Flavius Buzila – vocals, guitar
* Mihai Andritcu – violin
* Andrei Stoi – bass
* Andrei Balasa – guitar
* Nunu Racris – drums

